"title": "3221: Holy Spirit, and prayer",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3221: holy spirit, and prayer",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The Holy Spirit intercedes for God's people and also prompts their petitions, supplications and thanksgivings.</p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit enables God's children to address him as ``Abba''</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:15\">ROM 8:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6\">GAL 4:6</a></p>\n<h2>The role of the Holy Spirit in prayer</h2>\n<h3>He prompts supplication</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:10\">ZEC 12:10</a></strong> <em>“a spirit” (NIV text) or “the Spirit” (NIV footnote).</em></p>\n<h3>He inspires prayers of praise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:21\">LUK 10:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:18-Eph5:20\">EPH 5:18–5:20</a></p>\n<h3>He inspires praying in tongues</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:4\">ACT 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:44-Acts10:46\">ACT 10:44–10:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:6\">ACT 19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:14-1Cor14:18\">1CO 14:14–14:18</a></p>\n<h3>He intercedes for believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:26-Rom8:27\">ROM 8:26–8:27</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The evidence of the Holy Spirit's work prompts praise and thanks</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:2-1Thess1:5\">1TH 1:2–1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:15-Acts11:18\">ACT 11:15–11:18</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are exhorted to pray in the Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:18-Eph6:20\">EPH 6:18–6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:20\">JUD 1:20</a></p>\n<h2>The love of the Holy Spirit is a motive for prayer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:30-Rom15:32\">ROM 15:30–15:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:13\">LUK 11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:14-Acts8:17\">ACT 8:14–8:17</a></p>",
